## Tier transitivity (the deep cut)

When the cached upstream wiki column description already carries a tier suffix like
`(Tier 1 тАФ Trade.PositionTbl)`, Phase 5 inherits that tag **verbatim** for the passthrough column in the downstream object тАФ it does NOT change to `(Tier 1 тАФ main.dwh.gold_sql_dp_prod_we_dwh_dbo_fact_customeraction)`. The Synapse mirror is a RELAY, not the origin.

Same rule applies down the UC chain:

- `Fact_CustomerAction.HistoryID` says `(Tier 1 тАФ History.Credit)` (origin).
- `gold_sql_dp_prod_we_dwh_dbo_fact_customeraction.HistoryID` тАФ relay, inherits `(Tier 1 тАФ History.Credit)`.
- `v_fact_customeraction_enriched.HistoryID` тАФ relay, inherits `(Tier 1 тАФ History.Credit)`.
- `v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.HistoryID` тАФ relay, inherits `(Tier 1 тАФ History.Credit)`.
- `de_output_etoro_kpi_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.history_id` (renamed) тАФ relay with rename, inherits `(Tier 1 тАФ History.Credit)` plus a `renamed from HistoryID` note.

See `GATE-lineage-contract.mdc` for the full transitivity rules.

## Gate тАФ Phase 3 тЖТ Phase 4

Phase 4 requires every upstream UC object the source code references to have an entry in `_discovery/upstream_wikis/_index.json` тАФ either a cached wiki or a `_NO_WIKI__` placeholder. If any upstream is missing entirely from the index, the routing pass was incomplete.

Phase 4 also requires that no upstream is in `blocked_on_upstream: true` state. If one is, document the upstream first (return to Phase 0 for that upstream's schema if not yet schema-carded; otherwise jump straight to Phase 1 for the missing upstream).

## Anti-patterns

- тЭМ Treating the gold-mirror table as an origin. It's a relay тАФ always inherit through to the Synapse base table's origin tag.
- тЭМ Skipping the bronze-pure-ingest route ("we don't have the DB_Schema repo locally") тАФ even if you can't read the production wiki, recording the routing decision so the wiki gap is visible is the value-add.
- тЭМ Copying the upstream wiki's `_index.json` instead of the wiki body. The body is what Phase 5 inherits FROM.
- тЭМ Re-querying `system.access.column_lineage` here. That's Phase 2's job; this phase is offline-only.
